nodes.text: Darth Wrend was a Sith Lord of the reconstituted Sith Empire.

Darth Wrend was intended to appear in Star Wars: The Old Republic with a connection to Jaesa Willsaam's story, but was ultimately cut. The character exists within the game files with a placeholder model.

An ancient Sith Lord named Darth Wrend has since been mentioned in the 2019 canon novel Master & Apprentice. It is currently unknown whether there is a connection between the two identically-named characters.
